<section id='ExecUseShell'>
<title>ExecUseShell</title>

<command>
<cmdsynopsis>
	<arg choice='plain'>ExecUseShell [shell]</arg>
</cmdsynopsis>
</command>

<para>Makes the
<fvwmref cmd="Exec"/>
command use the specified shell, or the value of the
<emphasis remap='I'>$SHELL</emphasis>
environment variable if no shell is specified, instead of the
default Bourne shell
(<filename>/bin/sh</filename>).</para>

<programlisting>
ExecUseShell
ExecUseShell /usr/local/bin/tcsh
</programlisting>


</section>
